title: Nurse Sydney Sutherland brutally abducted, raped, and killed while jogging near home
itunes:title: Nurse Sydney Sutherland brutally abducted, raped, and killed while jogging near home
description:
Nurse Sydney Sutherland has a route that she jogs regularly, but on August 19th, she disappears. Days later, her body is found and an arrest is made in her brutal rape and murder. Who killed Sydney Sutherland?

Joining Nancy Grace Today:

  • Jason Oshins - New York Defense Attorney
  • Caryn Stark - NYC Psychologist,
  • Donald Schweitzer - Former LA detective, Criminal Defense, Former Prosecutor 
  • Joe Scott Morgan - Professor of Forensics Jacksonville State University, Author of "Blood Beneath My Feet"
  • Ray Caputo - Lead News Anchor for WDBO Orlando
